Package: lan-chat
Version: 2.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: LAN Chat Team <lan-chat@local>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34), libstdc++6 (>= 11), libgcc-s1 (>= 11),
 libboost-system1.74.0,
 libsqlite3-0 (>= 3.37),
 libgtk-3-0 (>= 3.24),
 libwebkit2gtk-4.1-0 (>= 2.44),
 libnotify4 (>= 0.7),
 libjavascriptcoregtk-4.1-0
Description: LAN Chat - P2P Internal Network Instant Messenger
 A lightweight C++ P2P instant messaging tool for internal networks.
 No server required — each client discovers peers automatically via
 UDP broadcast and communicates directly over TCP.
 .
 Features:
  * True P2P — no central server needed
  * Automatic peer discovery (UDP broadcast)
  * Direct TCP connections between peers
  * Real-time messaging with sub-millisecond latency
  * Desktop notifications (libnotify)
  * Dark theme modern UI
  * Local message history (SQLite)
